title: BRIAN GABERMAN; 'A LIFE IN TRANSITION' BOOK RELEASE
description:
Last month's photo exhibit/signing for Element Advocate Brian Gaberman's book 'A LIFE IN TRANSITION' was a night to remember. We couldn't be more psyched on how the book came out, and are so proud of the hard work and dedication that Brian put into the creation of it from start to finish. 
Brian's photos looked amazing displayed on the walls of our new HQ "The Branch", and was accompanied by good friends, and musical performances by Tess Shapiro & Paul Kwon, Leo Romero's band Travesura, Evan Smith doing a solo gig, and Ray Barbee and the Mattson 2 (who literally shook the walls).
